<li><font color="#e00000"><strong>DRIVER IMPROVEMENT: Intel <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=fxp&amp;sektion=4">fxp(4)</a> cards with <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=nsphy&amp;sektion=4">nsphy(4)</a> could not negotiate and maintain 100mbit link. <a href="errata26.html#nsphy">A source code patch is available</a></strong></font>.
