<li><a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?">Many man page improvements.</a>
<li>Disable suffix removal code in <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=make&sektion=1&format=html">make(1)</a>, since it is buggy.
<li>Fix blink and underline attribute handling for new <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=scon&manpath=OpenBSD+2.7&arch=i386">PC display mode</a>.
