a193 23
<li>For <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=open&sektion=2&format=html">open(2)</a>, support O_FSYNC better.
<li>For <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=open&sektion=2&format=html">open(2)</a>, add a O_NOFOLLOW flag for dealing with symbolic links.  This should not be used by generic software -- only use this for very rare and specific problems.
<li><a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=traceroute&sektion=8&format=html">traceroute(8)</a> gets a new option, -f skips early node checks.
<li>Fix &quot;freeing free block&quot; panics.
