<li>Document our new <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=ipsec&sektion=4&format=html">ipsec(4)</a> <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=bridge&sektion=4&format=html">bridge(4)</a> stuff.
